VERSION
-------

@{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
     VERSION

@{b}DESCRIPTION@{ub}
     VERSION returns the version information of Filer.

@{b}ARGUMENTS@{ub}
     None.

@{b}RESULT@{ub}
