@Next "UF_RX_READLEFTDIR"
@Prev "UF_RX_READSOURCEDIR"
@Toc "UF_RX"

READTARGETDIR
-------------

@{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
     READTARGETDIR DIR/A

@{b}DESCRIPTION@{ub}
     READTARGETDIR reads the specified directory in the inactive
     directory listview. If the directory is read successful the
