READDROPDIR
-----------

@{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
     READDROPDIR

@{b}DESCRIPTION@{ub}
     READDROPDIR checks wether the first selected entry in the active
     @{"directory listview" Link "UF_MW_LV"} is a directory. If this is the case it will
     read that directory in the other directory listview.

@{b}ARGUMENTS@{ub}
     None.

@{b}RESULT@{ub}
     None.

@{b}CONFIGURATION EXAMPLE@{ub}
     DRAGANDDROPDIR "ALT LEFTBUTTON","READDROPDIR"

