UP
--

@{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
     UP

@{b}DESCRIPTION@{ub}
     UP moves the visible region of the active directory listview one
     step up. The cursor is only moved if it's on the lower end of the
     visible region.

@{b}ARGUMENTS@{ub}
     None.

@{b}RESULT@{ub}
     None.

@{b}CONFIGURATION EXAMPLE@{ub}
     KEY "NUMPAD 8","UP"

@{b}SEE ALSO@{ub}
     @{b}@{ub} @{"DOWN" Link "UF_RX_DOWN"}, @{"CURSORUP" Link "UF_RX_CURSORUP"}


@EndNode

