PAGEUP
------

@{b}SYNOPSIS@{ub}
     PAGEUP

@{b}DESCRIPTION@{ub}
     PAGEUP moves the visible region of the active directory listview
     one page up.  If the cursor gets out of the screen it's moved to
     the lower end of the visible region.

@{b}ARGUMENTS@{ub}
     None.

@{b}RESULT@{ub}
     None.

@{b}CONFIGURATION EXAMPLE@{ub}
     KEY "NUMPAD 9","PAGEUP"

@{b}SEE ALSO@{ub}
     @{b}@{ub} @{"PAGEDOWN" Link "UF_RX_PAGEDOWN"}, @{"CURSORPAGEUP" Link "UF_RX_CURSORPAGEUP"}


