Other topics
************

Updates
=======

   Whenever a new release of Filer gets released, I will post some
information in the appropriate newsgroups of some electronic networks.
The new archive will soon be available on many bulletin boards and on
all @{b}Aminet@{ub} FTP servers.  Major releases will also come with some PD
disks.


@EndNode

